Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐要去留学？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想相信  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是千真万确的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找春香姐姐问个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  别去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  你想你要是这么一问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以春香那性格  肯定会为了我们而放弃留学的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  拜托你说话经过大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可关系到春香的前程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们这两个妹妹而放弃这么好的机会真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想以春香的才能  日本实在是太狭小了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对国际型人才春香来说  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可遇不可求的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…可是  但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香还没告诉你们  就是因为她还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果春香真的决定去留学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望夏奈你也能支持她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  就热情地守护着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊  我们做妹妹的应该为她新的人生而庆祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  让我们笑着送她走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:15.64,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8}第13碗  大家在一起、承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是位于非洲的柏彭巴王国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里可以看到很多的野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:26.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近游客络绎不绝  非常热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  好想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香做的饭可是世界最好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃上这饭的人也就是世界最幸福的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃  煮得真是恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  听说春香姐姐要去留学  是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈告诉我的  吓了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊  我也想去外国看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎  伦敦  纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南极  四川省  亚马逊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么选择法…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是企鹅  熊猫和森蚺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（亚马逊森蚺：当今世界上最大的蛇，最长可达十米，重达二百二十五公斤以上）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么春香姐要扔下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有带上你的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过春香姐真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们这些人的大脑构造完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…们？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐一定会变得更加出色  然后回国的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点就选在学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有千秋的朋友要来  在别的地方比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是春香家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  想让她大吃一惊就得选个更神奇更出人意料的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大吃一惊的必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  普普通通的多无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…陪速水前辈你胡闹的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在玩儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香要去留学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…首先就是护照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀…看来我要做的准备工作还真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到会这样分开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  不管夏奈你去多远的地方  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都还是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会写信给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是我  要走的是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子哟  你似乎很失望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我希望春香能安心的走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家务事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  目前为止所有的家事都是春香一手包办的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了春香我们什么也干不成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然从你嘴巴里说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定要让她看看只有我们俩照样也能做得井井有条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过夏奈你们没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是有「sa si su se so」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa si su se so？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…圭子她说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家务事的基本就是「sa si su se so」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能做好那些  我想春香姐姐也会认同你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa si su se so是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是做好家务事的缩略语…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa…飒爽地？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,si…振作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ri…苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈  什么急事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa si su se so到底是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa si su se so不就是sa si su se so吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家务的sa si su se so
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我好像听过  记得so是扫除  类似这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so是扫除的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,se就是洗涤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是水洗厕所呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烹饪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sa的话  应该是裁缝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是si了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道  是管教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有空啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不为例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯  那就这样  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始执行作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是我们亲手做好一顿饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过为期一天的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做出能打动春香味觉的美味佳肴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  希望各位能鼎力支持
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了春香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训只是做饭就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有饭菜是没办法混过去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比什么都练  结果一无所成的强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛辣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  忍不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责试吃的各位请坦诚地提出意见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是没问题  不过让我们尝的东西能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  春香姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托真希请她参加排球比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上才会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要是春香在的话  秘密特训还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经着迷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指之间粘粘的  这样粘粘的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有焦味！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  火太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是增稠料太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  试吃品一号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉松吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名为…肉松堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们尝过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那不是你们的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让肉散开  到底是揉得不够还是材料不够…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  请务必试下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次没碎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…总觉得这弹性很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…很有咬劲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…材料胡搅一通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧着了  烧着了啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不  这是火烧啊火烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:14.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（火烧：法式菜肴上桌时点火燃烧酒中的酒精成分）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火烧是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子？还是说调味料？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  都要为了春香做出美味的汉堡肉饼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我心里已经快放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  春香…是为了春香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻饼堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（荻饼：将梗米和糯米混煮轻搅成后揉成团，再敷上一层黄豆粉制成）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦炭堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着只要抽去空气  就不容易散了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到突破口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  保持这个状态进入第三局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟能生巧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  材料弄成这样已经完美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐她也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边找到门路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩你那火候的掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  一定做出完美的汉堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光烧饭就那么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有扫除和洗衣服什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香可是一个人做了所有家事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会被选为留学生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天  就我们两个来做家务…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香回来时一定会变得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成世界级头儿的超级春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要笑着送她走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  吵到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见  在扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐请继续睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  扫除洗涤所有的家事我们包了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是姐姐的感谢日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太明白  那可以拜托你们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  洗涤剂要放多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶子上不是写着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢你  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在晃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必须就我们俩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快把冬马和阿真变厕所蹲才学成的汉堡肉饼做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到最后的步骤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  我认真起来还不是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能高兴实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到夏奈和千秋居然主动做家务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真的很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这样一来春香也可以安心上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我们家务也能做  不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  说好笑着送她的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  我不要你去留学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去…外国啊  别去啊  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  你那样犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…太狡猾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从谁那儿听说我要去留学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希说你要去留学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去留学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得我会扔下你们这样走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:51.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次航班將在19点到达圣弗朗西斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您旅途愉快
